{"tid":1164703,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[非劇透]GoT嘅爛尾，係咪更加奠定咗Breaking Bad嘅神劇地位？","createTime":"2019-05-21T09:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T18:07:49.000Z","uid":8394,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb8d58ddbd6a937a8f88f0015498286ba1d59f8","tid":1164703,"uid":8394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:52:59.000Z","msg":"尋日睇完 GoT finale 有感而發<br />\n好記得GoT頭幾季真係好令人驚豔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾年成日有人拎佢嚟同 Breaking Bad 比<br />\n啲外國媒體經常爭辯邊套係美劇第一<br />\n<br />\n但經過GoT嘅失望埋尾<br />\n係咪更加奠定咗Breaking Bad嘅神劇地位<br />\n故事邏輯嚴謹  發展合理<br />\n人物行為又符合設定同合理真實<br />\n角色嘅成長同心理描寫又做得好好<br />\n節奏掌控、鏡頭呢啲都係大師級<br />\n<br />\n其實GoT頭幾季真係好正<br />\n係絕對有得同 Breaking Bad 一拼<br />\n例如 Red Wedding 雖然突然同驚訝<br />\n但諗返又幾合理（符合 Walder Frey 嘅性格同作風）<br />\n成個故事發展係出乎預期但又合乎常理之內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知近兩三季可以完全失晒控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變咗近乎 TVB 嘅劇情同邏輯<br />\n好多巴打都有討論唔使再多講<br />\n<br />\n我就兩套都好鐘意<br />\n但見到 GoT 變成咁真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而對 Breaking Bad 嘅欣賞同喜愛就更上一層樓<br />\nGoT 劇情自從冇原著跟之後大暴走<br />\n更加令我佩服 Vince Gilligan 同憎恨 D&amp;D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對 GoT 好失望嘅巴絲打<br />\n我推介你哋睇 Breaking Bad <br />\n我相信呢套劇唔會令你失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過 GoT 整體嚟講都係一套高質嘅美劇<br />\n調整好心理接受最後兩三季嘅質素都值得一追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6rTxdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6rTxdz.png&h=47fac93a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e890d322b48f4a728421abd7df8f858f9cb179bc","tid":1164703,"uid":193436,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":